main event: A UFO was reported over Baltimore, Maryland, described in hand-drawn sketches.
interesting points: The sketches depict a UFO in the sky along with buildings,The first sketch includes two close-up views labeled 'SEEN CLOSE' and 'SIDE VIEW',The second sketch provides a nighttime scene with additional close-up views of the object,Both sketches are labeled with references that suggest they are part of an exhibit,The report includes two pages of sketches but no traditional photographs.
